PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?tvShowTitle WHERE {
  fb:m.08l257 fb:tv.tv_personality.tv_regular_appearances ?appearance .
  ?appearance fb:tv.tv_regular_personal_appearance.program ?tvShow .
  ?tvShow fb:type.object.name ?tvShowTitle
  FILTER ( LANG( ?tvShowTitle ) = 'en' )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT ?championship WHERE {
  fb:m.0jnq8 fb:sports.sports_team.championships ?championship .
  ?championship rdfs:label ?label .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?label ) = 'en' ) .
  BIND( SUBSTR( ?label , 1 , 4 ) AS ?year ) .
  FILTER ( STRSTARTS( ?label , "20" ) ) .
  BIND( xsd:integer ( ?year ) AS ?yearInt )
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?yearInt )
LIMIT 1
